569
00:48:52,373 --> 00:48:53,623
Taedong River 1.

570
00:48:56,953 --> 00:48:58,663
So this is how we finally meet.

571
00:49:00,423 --> 00:49:05,043
To catch you,
I've been to Berlin, Munich, Frankfurt,

572
00:49:05,133 --> 00:49:06,553
and Warsaw.

573
