721
01:01:15,109 --> 01:01:17,489
Jang Han-na,
you're banned from this scene.

722
01:01:18,489 --> 01:01:21,279
Until ordered otherwise,
go stay in the office.

723
01:01:21,369 --> 01:01:22,909
